{
  "stem": "27.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from then on, there was no more-- worked and when we got down in the mine, they asked us, what kind of engineer are you?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What kind of engineer are you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, chemical, this one?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I told them general.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What am I going to-- I wasn't an engineer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was I? 20 years old?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't an engineer, and my brother was 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "General engineer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "OK, general engineer, you're fine, stay here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I became an electric welder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, laying on your back, no mask protection, and was welding the pipes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, some type of pipes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They showed you where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No, you didn't have to be a genius to do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They have to show you once, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But my eye was killing me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, to go back, when I came back to Prague, I was blind on one eye, left.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when I went to the doctor in Prague, he told me you're never going to see out of your left eye.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He said never.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's gone, burned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The retina is burned, everything, and there's nothing I can do for you because glasses won't help either.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And by miracle, a week later, I just opened my eye, and I seen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I never had trouble since that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When I told the doctor here about it, I mean, here in the USA, he said well, this was a miracle because when the retina is burned you are blind.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he asked how did you burn your retina?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I told him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Oh, he says, that's different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I worked three or four days, I worked in that kommando, the next day another commando, third day another, but very seldom with my brothers.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
